    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of the African Pygmy ethnic group of the same name currently inhabiting the southeast Ituri Forest region of Zaire.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
